{"tid":1831550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁講，其實勇武需要一個大台（預咗俾人屌）","createTime":"2020-01-20T12:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T13:11:55.000Z","uid":135493,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"788e69715b256c69d6c54f1c74ad6c81f60c3dc9","tid":1831550,"uid":135493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"我知大台呢個詞語會俾人屌到仆街，但過去呢幾個星期感覺覺得，前線無一個commander 係好撚大獲。<br />\n<br />\n每一次我都喺現場，咩位置唔撚講，但聽到嘅訊息到撚亂，一個話左一個話右，相反對面嘅黑警一早部署好晒，圍撚住晒成個中環，面勇武根本唔知邊個位可以突破。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打仗一直都係揾邊個突破點而殺出重圍，其實琴日有幾幾千人，要走要打根本唔係問題，重點係邊個位打，兵貴神速，呢刻打唔入就收皮，其餘嘅人亦都會走唔到，我明白大台好可怕，但無人可以指揮大家邊度突破，最終出現嘅係圍捕TK，咁唔係更加大檸樂咩...."},{"pid":"1ecff0d2f6020d1ffc2a760bda02146cecc61892","tid":1831550,"uid":45753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"咁易咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2d5e493ea35d5cd086c199d42a40e84f28e17f","tid":1831550,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"但香港咁細 有大台出咗名之後 佢地點匿藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b66352067959881a31746f7fb0f9c458dbbc502","tid":1831550,"uid":272976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"咁講，和理非大台就拉<br />\n勇武大台下場係點你估下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係多謝你嘅意見<br />\n<br />\n現場行多兩步自己睇下啦鳩企咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5d3913c00b3340c0298e6b803da444ce61d9c5","tid":1831550,"uid":263261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"最有資格做領導個個坐緊監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992a35b2a253625f6ecd321920c5c6a47f53b5d2","tid":1831550,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"你要嘅唔喺大台<br />\n喺英雄"},{"pid":"152271b9ba83c7974f37fdb2c9271c92462a91c5","tid":1831550,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"要將軍"},{"pid":"85b0ac18e5ae2cce7fb11902b7f05fff99f3509f","tid":1831550,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"將軍咪天琦，可惜行太前"},{"pid":"f6b3bff1ccd9f6e0d22978561711cac6ff0bf884","tid":1831550,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"指揮&ne;大台"},{"pid":"d2b9e906b2fb04faae1983f94eb7cf588f46b940","tid":1831550,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"愛埃塔<br />\n<br />\n搞海外軍火庫，訓練營"},{"pid":"91e127f1d4fb4fb671435e77cff3d666b31666f4","tid":1831550,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"不如你直接講要個孫中山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係支持勇武有大台嘅，有哂行動目的果類，但我諗你未開始已經俾狗拆緊"}]}